52:19.840 --> 52:20.920
<i>How come?</i>

52:23.320 --> 52:24.320
<i>Why not?</i>

52:25.640 --> 52:27.480
<i>My partner and I had been close.</i>

52:29.520 --> 52:31.520
<i>We'd worked together for a long time.</i>

52:34.080 --> 52:36.600
<i>Failure to report misconduct,</i>

52:36.680 --> 52:39.320
<i>would you consider that
a criminal offense?</i>

52:40.640 --> 52:44.680
<i>Failing to report misconduct
in the department is a criminal offense.</i>

52:44.760 --> 52:45.760
<i>I'm aware of that.</i>

52:46.880 --> 52:48.240
<i>They call it blue code.</i>

52:49.160 --> 52:51.960
<i>You protect your partner
even though he's committing a crime.</i>

52:52.880 --> 52:55.560
