Open the fucking door!

01:01:55.000 --> 01:01:56.000
What do you want?

01:01:57.480 --> 01:01:59.600
Okay, quit fucking around. Come on.

01:01:59.680 --> 01:02:00.680
Open the door.

01:02:01.320 --> 01:02:03.880
I know you're out there. What do you want?

01:02:08.880 --> 01:02:11.680
What's going on? Come on, open up!

01:02:11.760 --> 01:02:13.400
What the fuck is this?

01:02:32.720 --> 01:02:34.560
Open the fucking door!

