01:10:34.560 --> 01:10:37.240
Eddie, are you alright in there?

01:10:37.320 --> 01:10:39.360
Eddie, is everything okay?

01:10:39.440 --> 01:10:40.840
Eddie, open up!

01:10:42.720 --> 01:10:44.600
Damn, what a stench.

01:10:45.920 --> 01:10:47.960
You'd better come
take a look at this.

01:10:53.120 --> 01:10:54.760
What have you done to her?

01:10:54.840 --> 01:10:56.440
What have you done to Rose?

01:10:57.840 --> 01:11:00.760
Get down on the floor and don't you move.
Get down!

01:11:00.840 --> 01:11:01.840
Ooh!

