01:12:21.760 --> 01:12:24.560
<i>I'm Detective Edward Robert Sutton.</i>

01:12:26.080 --> 01:12:29.040
<i>Badge number 5149.</i>

01:12:31.000 --> 01:12:35.280
<i>I've served with honour,
